title: {GODPROP #2} CATNIP on Acres
body:
# If this proposal passes:
1. ECHO-FTM ZOODEX LP will be added to the incentivized pairs for Yorocoon. >> https://dex.zoocoin.cash/farms
2. CATNIP will be added as a single stake pool on Acres https://acres.maxus.blog
# If you vote yes, select one of the options:
The CATNIP pool on Acres will earn Acres at:
1. Highest Rate (= gDeli / Acres / ECHO)
2. Middle Rate (= Hyper LPs)
3. Low Rate (= Sushi LPs)
choices: No, I have poopy in my diaper.
